        public BulkLoaderVertexProgram.Builder keepOriginalIds(boolean keepOriginalIds)
        Specifies whether the original vertex identifiers should be kept in the target graph or not. In case of false BulkLoaderVertexProgram will add another iteration to remove the properties and it won't be possible to use the data for further incremental bulk loads.
